{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You're a spirit dwelling in a highschool, with the power to pick souls to live with you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cherry is ripe for the picking, but before your power will work you must discover why she's ripe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your task: listen to the gossip around the school, and delve into the hearts of her peers, to uncover the truth about Cherry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/continue.png?t=1732065688\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You play as <strong>Kimiko</strong>, a decisive and powerful spirit, with the ability to harvest shadows - bring across the living into her world of spirits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/dusk3gif.gif?t=1732065688\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You must work together with two spirits:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/Mokoto.png?t=1732065688\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/Emi.png?t=1732065688\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The living are called shadows as to the spirits the living appear without light or color.  The closer the shadows are to the spirit world the brighter and more colorful they appear.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/gifdark.gif?t=1732065688\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Harvest&quot; is used to describe the ability to bring a very bright and colorful shadow over to the spirit world - when they are ripe for the picking. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/aboutgame.png?t=1732065688\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This Visual Novel has a &quot;VTuber&quot; anime style, and integrates stills from 3D models into the scenes and plot, for an absorbing 2.5D Adventure Game gameplay. With branching story lines, enjoy broad replayablity and walk the roads less traveled to unlock achievements you will be dying to share.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">About 90% of the playtime is spent in visual novel, with the 2.5D sections deepening your choices for the non-linear gameplay: You can choose how to answer, but also who to talk to, and when. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/extras/kimikogifsteam.gif?t=1732065688\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732065688","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732065688","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/2d475e892c12158b55906ce39b8b5a131da5f89e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732065688","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206100/2d475e892c12158b55906ce39b8b5a131da5f89e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732065688","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Implied accidental death and discussions of ghosts/spirits in afterlife. "},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You're a spirit dwelling in